psychology.

34:01.957 --> 34:03.500
There's nothing wrong
with wanting to know

34:03.500 --> 34:05.001
what makes you tick.

34:05.001 --> 34:06.670
You can't figure out
who someone else is

34:06.670 --> 34:09.923
until you figure out yourself.

34:09.923 --> 34:11.967
